title: Football Roundup: Crestline downs St. Joseph
text:
Football Roundup: Crestline downs St. Joseph 12:14 a.m. EDT October 17, 2015 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Crestline 36, St. Joseph 22 
J.C. Clark rushed for 132 yards on 26 carries and scored a touchdown and J.R. Wolfe ran for 78 yards and two touchdowns and passed for another score Friday night as Crestline downed Fremont St. Joseph. Wolfe completed six of 17 passes for 83 yards. Ty Clark had four receptions for 27 yards and Davon Triplett had two catches for 42 yards and a touchdown for Crestline. Read or Share this story: http://ohne.ws/1RNE6cP TOP VIDEOS
